<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="http://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.4/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.11.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="http://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.4/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/javascripts/goalbuddies.js"></script>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <% include header.ejs %>
          
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <div class="jumbotron">
                <h1>Goal Buddies</h1>
                <h2><small>Achieve more goals, faster, together</small></h2>
            </div>
            
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-1"></div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="well">
                        <h4>Did you ever lose motivation halfway through a goal?
                        Never actually completely finish your New Year's Resolution?
                        We (and your friends) can help you do that!</h4>
                        <p>Goal Buddies is an application on Android and on the web 
                        that allows basic goal tracking functionality. However, in 
                        addition to that, your friends can keep you motivated by 
                        sending you personalized reminders about your upcoming 
                        goals, so that you can boast about your heroic achievements
                        on time!</p>
                        
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="panel panel-default">
                        <div class="panel-heading">Global Statistics</div>
                        <div class="panel-body">
                            <p>Total Goals: <%= /*totalGoals*/ %></p>
                            <p>Goals completed: <%= /*goalsCompleted*/ %></p>
                            <p>Days Saved: <%= /*daysSaved*/ %></p>
                            <p>Motivations offered: <%= /*timesMotivated*/ %></p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-1"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
